How to check if `set_time_limit();` disabled
```
if (strpos(ini_get('disable_functions'), 'set_time_limit') === false) {
    set_time_limit(0);
}
```

@nokimaro It probably will not work, since `set_time_limit()` may be blocked by safe mode, not `disable_functions`. We probably need something like:

```php
@set_time_limit(0) or Yii::warning(...);
```
